headline: Procter & Gamble upgraded to Buy at Erste Group on Friday
summary: As previously reported, Erste Group upgraded Procter & Gamble to Buy from Hold following quarterly results. The firm notes P&G maintained its forecast for the financial year 2025. Accordingly, sales growth should amount to approx. +2% to 4%. The company also reiterated its growth forecast for expected annual earnings per share. Erste expects Procter & Gamble to exceed this targeted earnings growth rate, and says the stock is attractively valued compared to the sector. Published first on TheFly –
